data.description: STUNNING 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom 2 car garage POOL home located in one of Martin County's most desirable neighborhoods of North River Shores. LOW HOA $45/month. Boats welcome! Home situated on just over 1/3 of an acre corner lot with oversized driveway. 2021 5V crimp metal roof, 2021 fully fenced in backyard, 2022 AC & full home accordion storm shutters. Kitchen, dining & living room overlooking beautiful covered & screened in patio/pool, perfect for entertaining. Walking distance to river, major shopping, restaurants & several boat ramps. Easy access for boaters interested in living close to water!!
